---
import Layout from '@/components/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="CrewTactics" description="Overview, card deck, random card generator, and leader guides">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">CrewTactics</h1>
  <div class="prose lg:prose-xl mx-auto">
    <p>CrewTactics is a collection of practical leadership and communication exercises designed to be used during rucks and team training. Each card presents a specific tactic that leaders can practice to improve team cohesion, decision-making, and adaptability.</p>
    
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-6 mb-4">How It Works</h2>
    <p>Draw a card during your ruck to focus on a specific skill. Practice the tactic, reflect on the prompts, and discuss with your team. Regular use builds leadership muscle memory.</p>
    
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-6 mb-4">Categories</h2>
    <div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-700 rounded-lg p-4">
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Leadership</h3>
        <p>Exercises focused on leading teams, taking responsibility, and developing others.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-700 rounded-lg p-4">
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Communication</h3>
        <p>Techniques for clear, effective communication under various conditions.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-700 rounded-lg p-4">
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Decision Making</h3>
        <p>Frameworks and techniques for making better decisions, especially under pressure.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-700 rounded-lg p-4">
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Adaptability</h3>
        <p>Practices for staying flexible and adjusting to changing circumstances.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <p class="mt-6 text-center">
      <a href="/lead/crew-tactics/generator" class="btn btn-primary">Try the Tactics Generator</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</Layout>
